title: Cassiopeia W Bug
body: In a game playing against Cassiopeia and her W isn't showing up on the ground at all. Her cast animation goes off and then you can see where it goes or where it is on the ground.

replies.body:
This is a known bug in League. It's currently being worked on by Riot (not really though).

Bug reports belong [here](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report).
